Text: iShares S&P Mid-Cap 400 Value ETF (NYSEARCA:IJJ) declared a  -  dividend on Tuesday, September 24th, Wall Street Journal reports. Shareholders of record on Wednesday, September 25th will be given a dividend of 0.7434 per share on Monday, September 30th. This represents a yield of 1.7%.
